---
import Notebook from '../layouts/Notebook.astro';
import { SITE } from '../config';
---
<Notebook title="about me">
  <p>hi, i'm <strong>{SITE.name}</strong> — a junior at Boston University, CS and math,
     minor in history and linguistics (hopefully).</p>
  <br />
  <p>first-gen, headed to grad school. trying to reach for the moon one way or
     another. mostly interested in the robotics + ML + linguistics side of things —
     teaching machines to actually understand what people mean.</p>
  <br />
  <p>i also enjoy making my own games. lately i've been obsessed with recreating
     old discontinued ones — we fr need a market for games towards girls, like,
     what happened LOL.</p>
  <br />
  <p>i love talking about how everything is electric-powered and runs in binary
     at the bottom.</p>
  <br />
  <p>i started coding because my Minecraft was obnoxiously BAD and i wanted to
     fix it. now i enjoy <code>C++</code>, <code>C</code>, and <code>Rust</code>
     more than other languages. i do enjoy assembly tho.</p>
  <br />
  <p>in my free time i play fortnite. i also do bug bounty hunting to help pay
     rent — the real college life.</p>
  <br />
  <p>coffee order: a good dark roast with a hint of vanilla.</p>
  <br />
  <h2>find me</h2>
  <ul>
    {SITE.links.map((l) => <li><a href={l.href}>{l.label}</a></li>)}
    {SITE.emails.map((e) => <li>email: <a href={`mailto:${e}`}>{e}</a></li>)}
  </ul>
</Notebook>
